{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 39,
  "title": "第三十九章（法本）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "昔之得一者："
    },
    {
      "text": "天得一以清，"
    },
    {
      "text": "地得一以寧，"
    },
    {
      "text": "神得一以靈，"
    },
    {
      "text": "谷得一以盈，"
    },
    {
      "text": "萬物得一以生，"
    },
    {
      "text": "侯王得一以為天下正。"
    },
    {
      "text": "其致之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "天無以清將恐裂，"
    },
    {
      "text": "地無以寧將恐發，"
    },
    {
      "text": "神無以靈將恐歇，"
    },
    {
      "text": "谷無以盈將恐竭，"
    },
    {
      "text": "萬物無以生將恐滅，"
    },
    {
      "text": "侯王無以貴高將恐蹶。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故貴以賤為本，"
    },
    {
      "text": "高以下為基。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以侯王自謂孤、寡、不轂。"
    },
    {
      "text": "此非以賤為本邪？"
    },
    {
      "text": "非乎！"
    },
    {
      "text": "故致數車無車，"
    },
    {
      "text": "不欲琭琭如玉，落落如石。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "昔，往也。一，無為，道之子也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言天得一故能垂象清明。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言地得一故能安靜不動搖。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言神得一故能變化無形。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言谷得一故能盈滿而不絕也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言萬物皆須道以生成也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言侯王得一故能為天下平正。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "致，誡也。謂下六事也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言天當有陰陽弛張，晝夜更用，不可但欲清明無已時，將恐分裂不為天。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言地當有高下剛柔，節氣五行，不可但欲安靜無已時，將恐發洩不為地。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言神當有王相囚死休廢，不可但欲靈變無已時，將恐虛歇不為神。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言谷當有盈縮虛實，不可但欲盈滿無已時，將恐枯竭不為谷。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言萬物當隨時生死，不可但欲長生無已時，將恐滅亡不為物。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 13,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言侯王當屈己以下人，汲汲求賢，不可但欲貴高於人無已時，將恐顛蹶失其位。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 14,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言必欲尊貴，當以薄賤為本，若禹稷躬稼，舜陶河濱，周公下白屋也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-16",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 15,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言必欲尊貴，當以下為本基，猶築牆造功，因卑成高，下不堅固，後必傾危。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-17",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 16,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "孤寡喻孤獨，不轂喻不能如車轂為眾輻所湊。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-18",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 17,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言侯王至尊貴，能以孤寡自稱，此非以賤為本乎，以曉人。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-19",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 18,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 3
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "嗟嘆之辭。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-20",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 19,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "致，就也。言人就車數之為輻、為輪、為轂、為衡、為轝，無有名為車者，故成為車，以喻侯王不以尊號自名，故能成其貴。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-21",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 20,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "琭琭喻少，落落喻多，玉少故見貴，石多故見賤。言不欲如玉為人所貴，如石為人所賤，當處其中也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
